# Frontend Style Guide

- Prefer design system CSS variables from `src/styles/tokens.css`.
- Use BEM class naming: `block__element--modifier`.
- Reuse existing CSS classes for shared styles before adding new ones.
- Reuse common components when possible; avoid duplicate patterns.
- New UI sections go in their own file.
- New components go in their own file.
- Keep component files under ~200 lines; split into smaller components when it makes sense.

